snippet.title: 'GMA' Hot List: What parents should know about flat head syndrome
snippet.description:
Dr. Jennifer Ashton discusses what parents should know in the wake of Chrissy Teigen's viral post, and Amber Heard says she signed a lipstick to give to Michael Strahan.
